{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM01_OP1_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x2c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x12,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh!? Wh-Who are you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x205,
            "name_id": 0x1f,
            "extra_id": 0x216,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oink moo!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "There's no trace of it left... If it lasted a little longer, I could've analyzed it more."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh well, I guess it would spoil all the fun if this was too easy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "But then again, with a glowing flower and a glowing body...it's easy to make an educated guess."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "U-Umm, excuse me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "What is it? As you can see, I'm very busy, so please don't talk to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Umm, but...that's actually a grave... It's my little sister's."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...So please be gentle with it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Your little sister, was the girl from moments before?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yes! So, you could see her, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes, parts of it... Your voice travels a vast distance."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "So...I just followed your voice. I didn't mean to intrude."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Your sister seems to be in quite a predicament."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "To be living in such a state... This is the first time I've seen anything like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Living...? Does that mean that Nio is...safe?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x77,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Is there any way to help her? Oh, and who are you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Who knows? I am not obligated to tell you anything."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Besides, I assume that you're the owner of that workshop, am I right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "In that case, shouldn't you be able to come up with at least one solution?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "How do you know about the workshop...? And I don’t have any solutions..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hm? That's odd. Then you are not an alchemist?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "An...alchemist? What's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm an apothecary. I make medicine at my workshop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry for asking so many questions all at once!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Please...please tell me more about Nio!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cc,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "...Hmm, an apothecary? Then perhaps...it's very likely."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Listen, this is my fundamental philosophy..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Truths are not something that can be passed around by others. You, yourself, must demand and grasp them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1ce,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "If you want to know the truth, then you must study and think on your own. From what I can see, you are capable of that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I am?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Yes. However...it's not something you can blindly jump into."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "I shall give you two pieces of advice, though I have no obligation to do so. Take it as my apology for intruding."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1cf,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "First, as a means to finding your sister, you must study alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "So, what is alchemy? How do I‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "And second, this glowing flower‐you must understand it. That is all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Your sister is somewhere you can't reach with your hands."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "With alchemy, there are a number of different ways to bring her back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "This glowing flower...it doesn't look like a medicinal herb. What is it, exactly?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1d0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Don't ask me. Answer that question on your own. Well...farewell."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Oh...! Please wait! I have a few more questions!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "She herself doesn't seem to be aware of it... But I didn't expect to encounter alchemy in a place like this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "However, that girl... In her current state, I'd say she has about three years..."
        }
    ]
}